01:04:56.970 --> 01:04:59.820
I mean, one of the issues
with all the investment banks

01:04:59.820 --> 01:05:09.170
was if there is no downside--

01:05:09.170 --> 01:05:12.450
right-- you take
a huge position,

01:05:12.450 --> 01:05:14.970
that position comes through,
