So they want to-- you want
to give people incentives

01:05:41.050 --> 01:05:43.630
not to put companies at risk.

01:05:43.630 --> 01:05:45.970
You want to give
executives incentives

01:05:45.970 --> 01:05:49.150
not just to think
about the short term.

01:05:49.150 --> 01:05:50.525
It's a difficult matter.

